1.stateless functional component dont manage state but they do still allow for props
2.stateless functional component do not have access to 'this'
3.stateless functional component are faster than our class based component

example:

const User = (props) =>{
    return{
        <div>
            <p>Name : {props.name}</p>
            <p>age : {props.age} </p>
        </div>
    }
}

ReactDOM.render(<User namw='neha' age = {24} />,document.getElementById('app'));
